---
title: Trust Tier Evaluation — Incoming Message Flow
---
flowchart TD
    MSG[Incoming message\narrives at relay node]

    SIG{Valid cryptographic\nsignature from\nregistered identity?}
    MSG --> SIG

    SIG -->|No| DROP1["❌ Dropped at relay node\nNo delivery failure returned\nSender unaware"]
    SIG -->|Yes| BLOCK

    BLOCK{Sender pubkey on\npersonal blocklist\nor reputation feed?}

    BLOCK -->|Yes| DROP2["❌ Silently dropped at relay node\nNo notification to sender\nNo notification to recipient"]
    BLOCK -->|No| ALLOW

    ALLOW{Sender meets\nallowlist criteria?}

    ALLOW -->|Yes — contact list| PRIMARY["✅ Primary Inbox\nImmediate delivery"]
    ALLOW -->|Yes — org identity match| PRIMARY
    ALLOW -->|Yes — web-of-trust vouched| PRIMARY
    ALLOW -->|Yes — opted in to unknown senders| PRIMARY
    ALLOW -->|No| AUTO

    AUTO{Auto-resolution\nrules match?}

    AUTO -->|"≥ N whitelist contacts vouch\n(configurable, default 3)"| PRIMARY
    AUTO -->|"Org domain previously\nallowlisted"| PRIMARY
    AUTO -->|"Reputation score above\nconfigured threshold"| PRIMARY
    AUTO -->|No match| PENDING

    PENDING["⏳ Pending Queue\nSender identity displayed\nTrust provenance shown\nUser reviews"]

    PENDING -->|Accept + allowlist| PRIMARY
    PENDING -->|Accept this message only| INBOX_ONE["✅ Delivered once\nSender not allowlisted"]
    PENDING -->|Reject + ignore| DROP3["❌ Discarded\nNo notification to sender"]
    PENDING -->|Reject + blocklist| DROP4["❌ Discarded\nSender added to personal blocklist"]

    style DROP1 fill:#fee2e2,stroke:#ef4444
    style DROP2 fill:#fee2e2,stroke:#ef4444
    style DROP3 fill:#fee2e2,stroke:#ef4444
    style DROP4 fill:#fee2e2,stroke:#ef4444
    style PRIMARY fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#22c55e
    style INBOX_ONE fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#22c55e
    style PENDING fill:#fef9c3,stroke:#eab308
